author: maxb
msg: Merge r12006, r12136, r12146 from trunk to 1.1.x branch.
Fix issue 2124 - bugs in svn switch over ra-dav.
Changes made in the 1.1 client cause 1.0 and 1.1 servers to be
driven in a way that weren't able to handle, resulting in
working copies that *look* okay, but can actually send commits
to the wrong repository location (if able to commit at all).
r12006: Teach mod_dav_svn how to handle the new request.
r12136: Make sure there is a versioned entry before setting the property.
r12146: Work around for buggy 1.1.0/1.1.1 servers by disabling res. walk.
